    <stitle>INTERNATIONAL&#174; VT 365 DIESEL ENGINE - REAR COVER, FLYWHEEL, and POWER STEERING GEAR DRIVE -
        Installation - Power Steering and Fuel Pump Assembly
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="2">
        <title>Power Steering and Fuel Pump Assembly</title>
        <figure id="f2651336" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd16/D1604.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="312px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Figure 486. Power steering and fuel pump assembly</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">O-ring</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Check pump assembly for cracks, leaks or other signs of damage. Place a new O-ring on power
                steering and fuel pump assembly prior to installation.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install power steering and fuel pump assembly, with new O-ring, to rear cover.</para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f2651337" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd16/D1603.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="312px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Figure 487. Mounting bolts for power steering and fuel pump assembly</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install two M10 x 1.5 x 30 mounting bolts for power steering and fuel pump assembly. Tighten
                bolts to the standard torque .
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
